-- Denmark orders four banks to change credit card risk weights
-- 
-- Thu Jul 31, 2014 09:01AM EDT
-- None



COPENHAGEN, July 31 (Reuters) - Denmark's financial regulator has told Danske Bank <DANSKE.CO>, Jyske Bank <JYSK.CO>, Laan og Spar Bank <LASP.CO> and Nykredit Bank to change the risk weights they give to credit cards and overdraft facilities as part of their credit portfolios, an official said.

